      "body" : "Disabling listening does not in any way prevent other nodes from requesting\nblocks from you, it just results in fewer connections, and it makes it much\nless likely (but not impossible) that other nodes synchronize their history\nfrom you.\n\nIf you want to reduce bandwidth usage, the limiter is the way to go.\n",
